<DevelopmentPlan VERSION="0.2.0">
  <ArchitectureNotes>
    <objective>Build a staged pipeline: video → slide intervals (standalone) → notes + visual context → export. Each stage is an independent CLI command.</objective>
    <non-goal>No ASR, no cloud processing, no web UI.</non-goal>
    <risk-1>False slide splits due to cursor movement, webcam, or compression artifacts.</risk-1>
    <risk-2>GPU backend may not be available — CPU fallback must always work.</risk-2>
    <risk-3>detect-slides is the longest step (2-3 video passes). Notes and export are fast.</risk-3>
  </ArchitectureNotes>

